---
title: Carb Smart Middle Eastern-Inspired Double Beef Koftas with Feta and Radish Salad
description: Tender shawarma-seasoned koftas are served alongside a hearty spring mix salad with a sweet-yet-tart fig dressing in this simple and filling Middle-Eastern-inspired dinner.
